{"tid":1421282,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"打怪攻略","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:15:58.000Z","uid":121985,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5edf21a3c0e68abd08b5e38bb36390f7b74509b7","tid":1421282,"uid":121985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:38:27.000Z","msg":"以下係打機時遇到打怪副本嘅攻略：<br />\n<br />\n打怪盡量唔好打到見血，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為你唔可能知啲怪有冇毒</span></span>，如果唔好彩遇著隻毒怪，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢啲血係極有可能毒害你自己同隊友仲有啲補師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要有效地鎮壓啲怪，最好嘅辦法係合力幫佢地斷手斷腳打到不能自理，令隻怪想逃走都唔得。<br />\n<br />\n怪物都係利字當頭，返到巢穴當然要boss俾額外寶物同金幣俾佢回血，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢一點係重中之重</span></span>，剩係洗錢補血都夠班boss肉痛，每次蝕一千幾百個金幣寶物，boss仲邊會肯無止境地出怪呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假如怪物同boss傾唔掂數，分分鐘啲怪物仲會攻番轉頭添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於想要阻止唔俾打怪嘅勇者，奉勸你地一句，對敵人仁慈即係對自己殘忍，怪物唔單止會攻擊勇者，仲會攻擊村民㗎，城衛又只會縱容怪物行兇唔會幫手，唔敢打怪嘅就退去安全位置等其他勇者幫你打，你企喺後面吸經驗值等開寶箱冇人會怪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後提提大家，要保持理智，見好就要識收手，千祈唔好打死隻怪！</span></span>"},{"pid":"649cd376f7a61b5c352c41fc37ebb7f8f6ffe0d7","tid":1421282,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad9d8c74c1f54244aba307b13b30461ee8ff59b3","tid":1421282,"uid":121985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:00:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d935cfcb5dff2f4b1967e06179568f9745cb85ea","tid":1421282,"uid":121985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:13:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d8c3377cb22d64c04e6b89b79b5523edd73b341","tid":1421282,"uid":91817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85ff5be454f66d37175ac390ce1a9b028211dcb5","tid":1421282,"uid":91817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"香城online <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b57c260fc9d99894b561ddd7e588b8e1aac979","tid":1421282,"uid":121985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ccf6fa94bb06a1bdce99a81f76081e39078a1d32","tid":1421282,"uid":56015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:11:12.000Z","msg":"打怪唔好打死。但要打到佢一年半載內都還唔拖先掂"},{"pid":"ee21c532e181381e3e3c19e131203d12e082bd27","tid":1421282,"uid":121985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ccf6fa94bb06a1bdce99a81f76081e39078a1d32","tid":1421282,"uid":56015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:11:12.000Z","msg":"打怪唔好打死。但要打到佢一年半載內都還唔拖先掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:15:58.000Z","msg":"呢樣好緊要，打殘隻怪可以拖累對方boss，打死隻怪就只會累到自己友<br />\n所以必須保持理智，最好避開唔打隻怪個頭剩係專注打四肢"}]}